{"tid":1047594,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"林作俾張堅庭串完會唔會返屋企攬住老母哭？","createTime":"2019-03-05T05:21:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-08T01:51:40.000Z","uid":175032,"like":63,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"016127f6f7a2e6ee6ea0ab3d40b7b00d77acd798","tid":1047594,"uid":175032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ayr_RhOQ1tw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAyr_RhOQ1tw&d=aJy3RA7fpCa2KE6CQkcak5NY2w26zYPSLCKwhaLFqs8%3D&h=1ee14e78\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Ayr_RhOQ1tw</a><br />\n<br />\n張堅庭頻道 - 林作的學歷勢利觀，看扁別人但自己又不成功"},{"pid":"40871337ea585c515e44e5825b328f5d0d0900fc","tid":1047594,"uid":83052,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T10:48:26.000Z","msg":"林作有幾垃圾同失敗先會出黎做咁多年野仲打飛機 口裡說不身體卻很誠實<br />\n口講英雄莫問出處但開口埋口都係牛津同哈羅<br />\n好心你啦，我知你睇緊<br />\n口講唔介意網民講乜但自己就成件怨婦咁<br />\n有自信有能力嘅人唔需要attention seeking 嘅，有料嘅人地自然知<br />\n你當日係Sir Oswald Cheung嘅肢體語言都帶出左自己嘅自卑心<br />\n高不成低不就，出黎做野法律界最top嘅唔到你<br />\n做娛圈又唔係高大靚仔或有觀眾緣<br />\n你睇下你，有啲咩能力係比大多數人優勝？<br />\n有，就係有個好老母賺錢比你靠母幹<br />\n然後日日用牛劍個朵打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你有能力有本事嘅人地自然會欣賞<br />\n成隻小學雞咁搏大眾眼球只會影衰自己母校<br />\n以及反映你只係一個除左家人鋪排嘅學歷以外一無是處嘅群腳仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1303981953edb46c62dafe07468581eee2d100d4","tid":1047594,"uid":83052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:36:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"516cb71a910cec57bdfd88ec141e30b34b358dcc","tid":1047594,"uid":81190,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T13:45:59.000Z","msg":"媽媽，佢話我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji